                    <div class="absolute left-4 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-primary-200 dark:bg-primary-700"></div>
                    
                    <div class="relative pl-10 pb-10">
                        <div class="absolute left-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white">1</div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">数据采集</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">硬件设备通过传感器采集环境数据（空气温湿度、土壤温湿度、水箱水位、一氧化碳浓度等）。</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="relative pl-10 pb-10">
                        <div class="absolute left-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white">2</div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">数据传输</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">通过MQTT协议将采集的数据发送到服务器，MqttClient接收数据。</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="relative pl-10 pb-10">
                        <div class="absolute left-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white">3</div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">数据存储</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">DataController将接收到的数据保存到数据库中，以便后续查询和分析。</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="relative pl-10 pb-10">
                        <div class="absolute left-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white">4</div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">阈值判断</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Task组件将采集的数据与预设阈值进行比较，判断是否超出范围。</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="relative pl-10 pb-10">
                        <div class="absolute left-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white">5</div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">自动控制</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">根据阈值判断结果，在自动模式下执行相应的控制操作：</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                            <li>土壤湿度低时自动浇水</li>
                            <li>水箱水位低时自动补水</li>
                            <li>异常情况下触发蜂鸣器报警</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="relative pl-10">
                        <div class="absolute left-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white">6</div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">指令发送</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">通过MQTT协议将控制指令发送给硬件设备，执行相应的操作。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

